                "# The Magnetic Compass — Principles",
                "The magnetic compass is the fundamental direction-finding instrument on ships, required by SOLAS as the primary means of steering when all other systems fail. It works because a magnetised needle aligns itself with the **horizontal component** of the Earth's magnetic field.",
