                "**Shallow Water Effects:** At some ports, the shape of the tidal curve is distorted by shallow water. The ATT includes 'shallow water corrections' for affected ports (mainly in Volumes II and III). These corrections adjust the times and heights of predictions for the non-linear effects of shallow water on tidal propagation."
