                "• **RNC (Raster Navigational Chart):** A pixel-for-pixel digital scan of a paper chart. Looks like the paper chart on screen but has no object intelligence — it cannot trigger alarms or be queried. Does NOT meet SOLAS requirements for replacing the paper chart folio. An ECDIS using only RNCs is NOT equivalent to paper charts.",
