              body: "Purpose (2 marks): Prevent cargo tank atmosphere from entering the flammable range by maintaining O2 below 8%, thus preventing explosion during cargo operations.\n\nComponents (1 mark each for 8 marks):\n1. Scrubber — removes SO2, soot; cools flue gas\n2. Blower (fans) — forces IG to cargo tanks via deck main\n3. Deck water seal — non-return device; prevents vapour backflow\n4. P/V breaker — emergency relief; prevents tank over-pressure\n5. P/V valve (on each tank) — maintains positive pressure; prevents air ingress\n6. O2 analyser — continuous monitoring of O2 in supply\n7. IG main line (deck) — distributes IG to all tanks\n8. Isolation valves — allow individual tank isolation"
