                "**Stage 2 \u2014 Introduction of fresh air:** Using portable fans or a fixed system. The IGS itself may be used by isolating the scrubber and connecting fresh air intake to gas blowers (faster method). Air replaces inert gas, raising O\u2082 to >21% and reducing HC below 1% LEL for safe man-entry."
