                "**Tankscope (Infra-red HC detector):** Measures hydrocarbon gas in the 0\u201320% by volume range. Works in inerted or over-rich atmospheres where catalytic sensors cannot function.",
                "**Explosimeter (Catalytic combustible gas indicator):** Measures HC concentration below the LFL (below ~1% by volume) in non-inerted or lean atmospheres. Requires oxygen to function \u2014 cannot be used in inerted tanks.",
