              question: { q: "Before entering a pump room on a tanker, which atmosphere check is required?", options: ["O\u2082 above 8% only", "O\u2082 at least 20.9%, HC below 1% LEL, and toxic gases within limits", "CO\u2082 below 1%, O\u2082 above 15%", "Temperature below flashpoint of cargo"], correct: 1, explanation: "Pump room entry requires: O\u2082 \u2265 20.9% (normal breathing air), HC < 1% LEL (no explosion risk), toxic gases (H\u2082S, benzene) within limits. All three must be checked and recorded on a permit to work before entry." }
